body:
Concurring, as Mossop said earlier (in a now-collapsed-on-github bit), getAddonByID() returns a promise as well, so it should be possible to just do:

```js
let addon = await ...getAddonByID(addonId);
// do uninstall
```

to simplify this significantly.
